<inglise> Whereas, in the light of experience gained in applying Commission Regulation (EEC) No 618/90 of 14 March 1990 laying down rules for drawing up the annual inventory of agricultural products in public storage (2), as amended by Regulation (EEC) No 3077/92 (3), certain arrangements for the management of stocks should be redefined, with particular attention to the rules for evaluating and monitoring stocks of agricultural products placed in public storage; whereas Regulation (EEC) No 618/90 should be repealed; </inglise>
