<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> Documentary records of the entry, storage and removal of products serving as a basis for the preparation of the annual accounts referred to in Article 1 of Regulation (EEC) No 3492/90 shall be sent by the storekeeper to the intervention agency at least once a month. </inglise>
