<inglise> Article 5 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 5 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> The inspecting body or its representative shall draw up a report on each inspection carried out at least once a year, in accordance with Article 4 and Annex III. </inglise>
